---
import geet from '../assets/geet-avatar.png';
interface Props {
	title: string;

}

const { title } = Astro.props;
---
<div class="container">
  <div class="header-container">
      <h1>{ title }</h1>
      <div class="author-container">
        <img src={geet.src}>
        <p>Geet Khosla, CEO @ proemnial</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tag-container">
      <span>14.12.2023</span>
      <span>press release</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="content-container">
  <p>a trailblazing leader in artificial intelligence technology, celebrates the one-year anniversary of its groundbreaking digital product, [Product Name]. This cutting-edge solution is designed to transform the way researchers, academics, and professionals engage with scientific literature by providing efficient and insightful summarizations of complex papers.
    [Product Name] leverages state-of-the-art natural language processing algorithms to sift through intricate scientific texts, distilling key information and presenting it in a concise and digestible format. With the exponential growth of research output in various fields, [Product Name] emerges as an indispensable tool, enabling users to stay abreast of the latest developments in their respective domains without the overwhelming task of navigating through lengthy papers.
    
